Package: vantorr
Title: Different functions to access Maxar/Vantor satellite imagery
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Wild", , "mWild@worldbank.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The vantorr package is a client for the Maxar/Vantor Hub
    APIs, enabling programmatic access to high-resolution satellite
    imagery (e.g., WorldView, Vivid Basemaps, ARD). It provides functions
    for discovery, search (including STAC metadata),OAuth2 authentication,
    OGC service (WMS/WMTS) consumption, and data retrieval for remote
    sensing and GIS applications.
